          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "229-Th used in this work was obtained by milking of",
                "sample of 233-U. The stock was sufficiently old so",
                "that 228-Th (half life~1.9 year)practically",
                "decayed. The target 229-Th(~10 micro gram)was made by",
                "electro deposition from an aqueous 0.001 M  nitric acid",
                "solution on a 6.75 mg/cm*2 super pure aluminium foil.",
                "Amount  of 229-Th in each target was determined from",
                "the electro deposition efficiency."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TRD",
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In order to determine the absolute",
                "yields of the fission  products, a lexan track",
                "detector was taken in dilute solution of known",
                "concentration of 229-Th in a sealed polypropylene tube.",
                "HPGe detector connected to a PC based 4K MCA was used",
                "for gamma ray counting of fission products."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ABSFY",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Cumulative yields of 27 fission products have been",
                "determined in  229-Th(n,f) by using  recoil cather",
                "technique follwed by gama ray spectrometry.",
                "Absolute fission tields were arrived at from the",
                "fission rate  measured by track etch counting method."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The activities of different radionuclides at",
                "the end of  irradiation were calculated from the peak",
                "areas of their  characteristics gamma rays after",
                "correcting for the detection efficiency, gamma ray",
                "abundance and cooling times.",
                "The cumulative yield of the fission products were",
                "calculated from the gamma ray activity at the end of",
                "irradiation using the standard activation  equation."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "Errors given on the yields are due to counting",
                "statistics only."
              ]
            }
